pliance.</p> <p>Liferay has been Ippon&rsquo;s portal platform of choice since 2004 and has been implemented in large projects including a portal with the French Ministry of Defense and <a href=\"http://www.stadup.com\">www.Stadup.com</a>, a sports club management ASP. Ippon Technologies is proud to offer Liferay Portal consulting, training, development and support services to the francophone community.</p>]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"header-link\" type=\"text\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[http://www.ippon.fr]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"image-link\" type=\"text\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[http://www.ippon.fr]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"flow\" type=\"list\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[right]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"open-header-link-in-new-window\" type=\"boolean\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[true]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"open-image-link-in-new-window\" type=\"boolean\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[true]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n</root>', 'general', 'BASIC-ARTICLE', 'IMAGE-FLOW', SPECIFIC_TIMESTAMP_20070727235900, TRUE, 2, 'Joe Bloggs', FALSE, TRUE);
