ebundled portlets, Liferay Portal was decidely the best candidate. These portlets&nbsp;allowed the user of the &quot;Digital Magazine&quot; to have visual tools for editing their content. Through the CMS, the portal already had tools that separated editing and managing content. Additionally, it was easy to visually apply various layout templates to different parts of the &quot;Digital Magazine.&quot;<br /><br />Thanks to these portlets, the &quot;Digital Magazine&quot; is now an active section of the <em>Educacyl</em> portal. It has a professional look-and-feel yet is easy to use by non-technical people.</p>]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"full-image1\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"thumb-image1\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"full-image2\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"thumb-image2\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"full-image3\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"thumb-image3\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"full-image4\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"thumb-image4\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"full-image5\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"thumb-image5\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"full-image6\" type=\"image\">\n		<dynamic-content></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"thumb-image6\" type=\"image\">\n		<