vel/liferay_4_extension_environment_guide/onepage/\">One page</a><br />\n            <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://content.liferay.com/4.3/doc/devel/liferay_4_extension_environment_guide/multipage/\">Multi-page</a></td>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-link\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://content.liferay.com/4.3/doc/devel/liferay_4_extension_environment_guide.pdf\">PDF</a></td>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-link\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wiki.liferay.com/index.php/Liferay_4_Development_in_the_Extension_Environment_Contributions\">LiferayPedia</a></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-title\">Liferay Plugin Development Guide<br />\n            Extending Liferay with Portlets and Themes</td>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-link\">N/A</td>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-link\"><a href=\"http://docs.liferay.com/4.3/official/liferay-43-plugins-guide.pdf\">PDF</a></td>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-link\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wiki.liferay.com/index.php/Liferay_4_Theme_Development_Guide_Contributions\">LiferayPedia</a></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-title\">Liferay API (with sources)</td>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-link\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.liferay.com/web/guest/documentation/4_3/development/api\">Javadoc</a></td>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-link\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://umn.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/lportal/liferay-portal-doc-4.3.0.zip\">ZIP</a></td>\n            <td class=\"cd-docfiles-link\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wiki.liferay.com/index.php/Liferay_4_Javadoc_Contributions\">LiferayPedia</a></td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<p><a name=\"lifecasts\"></a></p>\n<h1>Lifecasts</h1>\n<p>There are not yet any lifecast videos specific for Liferay v4.3. Please refer to the <a href=\"@root_path@/web/guest/documentation/4_2/development#lifecasts\">Development Lifecasts