body=Name%0ATitle%0ACompany%0AQuestion%2FComment\">email us</a> with any questions or comments you may have. In the meantime:</span></p>\n<ul>\n    <li><span class=\"journal-content-article\">Take a look at our <a href=\"http://www.liferay.com/web/guest/products/\">Products</a> and <a href=\"http://www.liferay.com/web/guest/services\">Services</a> pages for more information.</span></li>\n    <li>Read our CEO, Bryan Cheung\'s, <a href=\"http://www.liferay.com/web/bcheung/home?p_p_id=33&amp;p_p_action=0&amp;p_p_state=normal&amp;p_p_mode=view&amp;_33_struts_action=%2Fblogs%2Fview\" target=\"_blank\"><b>blog</b></a> about the event</li>\n    <li>Download Liferay\'s whitepaper: <br />\n    <a href=\"http://www.liferay.com/c/document_library/get_file?p_l_id=1980&amp;folderId=633258&amp;name=DLFE-442.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><b>PORTAL BEST PRACTICES: <br />\n    Getting the Most out of Your Portal Initiative</b></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"header-link\" type=\"text\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[http://www.liferay.com/web/guest/about_us/events/gartnerpcc_baltimore]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"flow\" type=\"list\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[default]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"image-link\" type=\"text\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[http://www.liferay.com/web/guest/about_us/events/gartnerpcc_baltimore]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"open-header-link-in-new-window\" type=\"boolean\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[true]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"open-image-link-in-new-window\" type=\"boolean\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[true]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n</root>', 'announcements', 'BASIC-ARTICLE', 'BASIC-ARTICLE', SPECIFIC_TIMESTAMP_20070719182800, TRUE, 2, 'Joe Bloggs', FALSE, TRUE);
