faster, better, and cheaper.</p>]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n</root>', 'general', 'BASIC-ARTICLE', 'IMAGE-FLOW', SPECIFIC_TIMESTAMP_20080317033700, TRUE, 2, 'Joe Bloggs', FALSE, TRUE);
insert into JournalArticle (id_, resourcePrimKey, groupId, companyId, userId, userName, createDate, modifiedDate, articleId, version, title, description, content, type_, structureId, templateId, displayDate, approved, approvedByUserId, approvedByUserName, expired, indexable) values (4607, 4608, 14, 1, 2, 'Joe Bloggs', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, '3347', 1.0, 'Services-Training-Dalian_Main', '', '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n\n<root>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"sidebar-location\" type=\"list\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[right]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"sidebar-content\" type=\"text_area\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[<h2>培训日期</h2> <p>四月22日&mdash;25日</p> <h2>培训地点</h2> <p><br />大连Liferay软件有限公司<br />地址：大连市高新园区七贤路2号，嘉创大厦12层02 <!--<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hamptonsuitesskokie.com/\">Hampton Inn &amp; Suites Chicago Skokie Hotel</a><br />\n5201 Old Orchard Road<br />\nSkokie, IL 60077<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;saddr=ORD&amp;daddr=5201+Old+Orchard+Rd,+Skokie,+IL+60077&amp;sll=42.019715,-87.82218&amp;sspn=0.127785,0.31929&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;z=12&amp;om=0\">Directions from O\'Hare</a>--></p> <h2>课程安排</h2> <p><a href=\"@root_path@/web/guest/services/training/course_topics_chinese\">课程安排</a></p> <h2>登记方法</h2> <p>Email&nbsp; <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"mailto:wwang@liferay.com?subject=Dalian%20Public%20Training%20Registration\">wwang@liferay.com</a></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n	<dynamic-element name=\"main-content\" type=\"text_area\">\n		<dynamic-content><![CDATA[<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">概览</span></b><b style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b><b style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p><br type=\"_moz\" /></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Liferay </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">将在中国大连举行一次公开培训。主题包括</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">portlet </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">开发、用</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">EXT</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">环境定制</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">portal</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">、内容管理以及</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">themes</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p><br type=\"_moz\" /></o:p></span></p>    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">课程结束的时候您将能够熟练的运用</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Liferay</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">创建</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">portlets</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，自动创建服务层和持久层代码以及通过理解</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Liferay</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">设计模式有效的调试。</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p><br type=\"_moz\" /></o:p></span></p>    <p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0in; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 50%; text-align: left; line-height: 19.2pt; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;\"><b><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">最新版本</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  <p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0in; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 50%; text-align: left; line-height: 19.2pt; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">您能够学到</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Liferay Portal 4.4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">中最新的功能</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span><b><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p><br type=\"_moz\" /></o:p></span></b></p>    <p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0in; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 50%; text-align: left; line-height: 19.2pt; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;\"><b><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">实践培训</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">您将会得到您所需要的经历，所以在课程结束的时候请做好准备开发您自己的</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">portlets<o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p><br type=\"_moz\" /></o:p></span></p>    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">主题专家</span></b><b style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">此次课程将由设计软件的专家教授。</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p><br type=\"_moz\" /></o:p></span></p>    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">开发环境</span></b><b style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">虽然</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Liferay</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">可以在任何服务器和数据库中运行，但是我们将使用</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Tomcat</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> MySQL</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">以及</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Eclipse</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，因为这是最快速的安装配置。我们或许也会简单涉及其他应用程序服务器和数据库的安装。</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">参加培训人员要求</span></b><b style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">必须具有</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Java </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> Servlets</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的基本知识；</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">装有</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Windows XP</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">系统及无线网卡的笔记本电脑；</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">- </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">推荐系统需求：</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">2.0Ghz Core Duo, 2GB RAM<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white none repeat scroll 0% 50%; margin-left: 33pt; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 19.2pt; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>  <h2>&nbsp;</h2><h2>Overview</h2><p>Liferay will host a public training seminar in Dalian, China. Core topics include&nbsp;portlet development, customizing the portal with the extension environment, content management and themes.</p><p>By the end of the course you will know&nbsp;how to create portlets using Liferay best practices,&nbsp;auto-generate the service and persistence layer and debug effectively&nbsp;by&nbsp;understanding Liferay design patterns.</p><h2>Latest&nbsp;Release</h2><p>Come and learn about the&nbsp;latest&nbsp;features&nbsp;in&nbsp;Liferay Portal 4.4!</p><h2>Hands-On Training</h2><p>You\'ll get&nbsp;the experience you need, so that you\'ll be ready to develop portlets on your own&nbsp;by the end of the course.</p><h2>Subject Matter Experts</h2><p>The course will be led by the Liferay experts who designed the software.</p><h2>Development Environment</h2><p>Although Liferay runs on almost any server and database, we will&nbsp;be using&nbsp;Tomcat, MySQL and Eclipse because this is the fastest&nbsp;setup&nbsp;for development. We may also touch upon installation with other application servers and databases as well.</p><h2>Prerequisites</h2><p>Basic knowledge of Java and Servlets is required.</p><p>A&nbsp;laptop with Windows XP and a wireless card is required.<br />- Recommended system requirements: 2.0Ghz Core Duo, 2GB RAM</p>]]></dynamic-content>\n	</dynamic-element>\n</root>', 'general', 'BASIC-CONTENT-SIDEBAR', 'BASIC-CONTENT-SIDEBAR', SPECIFIC_TIMESTAMP_20080320221000, TRUE, 2, 'Joe Bloggs', FALSE, TRUE);
